data.description: Enjoy main floor living & mountain views from this Pueblo West home!! This home has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 1387 sq. feet of living space and sits on 1.08 acres. The spacious bedrooms have large closets and the primary bathroom has double vanities with a walk in shower. Living room is wired for surround sound.  Newer stainless steel appliances and the front loading washer & dryer are included.  Septic Inspection is completed! New metal roof was installed in 1/2021 & new 40 gallon hot water heater installed in 5/2021. There is a 13'x 11' shed with concrete floor, green house & chicken coop in the large fenced area in the back of the house. This home does need new carpet as it is reflected in the price.  Horses welcome!! Enjoy mountain views & the fire pit on the sprawling back patio! Easy commute to Colorado Springs and surrounding areas!!
